Things I just did:

1. Saw a weird quote on a purple shirt

2. looked it up because I had no reason to believe it wasn’t from Night Vale but also no reason to belive it was

3. Saw it was Gilmore Girls

4. Yelled a bunch about it

5. Ran to my room becuase of that

6. Heard Phil Lester say something

7. Came downstairs to watch Dan and Phil with my brother

8. Watched Hilda instead

9. Currently watching Hilda
